Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:anise
Pronunciation:
Notes: Mainly <i>Angelica</i> spp., esp. <i>Angelica montana</i> (formerly <i>A. gingidum</i>) but occas. poss.<i> Anistome</i>; in NZ, spp. ??Mainly SI. [Transf. and extended use of <i>aniseed</i>, the seed of anise.]formerly used as wild fodder plants (mainly wild angelica).
